02_01 - Using automatic updates and custom feeds
	- genesis in admin menu lets you have auto updates & notify you when you input your email
	   -- https://www.screencast.com/t/Gv2KGD7PWX
	- site.net/feeds (default URL - feeds)
	
02_02 - Selecting the default layout
	- Layout settings can be set under default layout
		- each post can also be set & override the default layout - https://www.screencast.com/t/RajISvHLfI
	
02_03 - Using a logo or text for your header	
	- genesis has it's filename & directory for your logo & you can overwrite this w/ your own logo - https://www.screencast.com/t/PxaCS9iF
		- this will automate whenever you choose to display image or text on your header area under the customizer
	- some child themes let's you customize like the header, and the header section under theme settings will disappear
		https://www.screencast.com/t/6Z0aN0uSp3
	
