06_04 - How to shop for a Genesis theme	
	- you can build your own child theme or buy a child theme for StudioPress
	- Bottomline, Genesis framework needs a child theme to work.
	- Choose a Child Theme Guideline - https://www.screencast.com/t/yu6vXsA9e
	
